Q1:
Public Opinion Survey
This survey is being conducted as part of an educational activity for the Summer Institute in Computational Social Science (https://compsocialscience.github.io/summer-institute/locations#2021) This survey will ask questions related to your opinions, your use of social media, and demographic information. The goal of the activity is to study public opinions. At the end of the project, we will remove individually identifying information and share the data with other researchers and students. If you are not comfortable having your de-identified responses shared, please do not participate in this survey. You are free to stop at any time or skip any opinion question that you want. If you have any questions please email K.lawall@lse.ac.uk.
By clicking "I agree" below you are indicating that you are at least 18 years of age, is a resident of the UK, have read the above, and agree to participate in this research activity.
